data.description:
Buyer financing fell through. New Furnace! $2500 Buyer credit for new carpet upstairs. 
Prepare to be captivated by this extraordinary 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom haven located in the highly sought-after community of Green Valley Ranch. Welcome to 19417 Randolph Place, where luxury living meets contemporary style, offering you the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Step into this elegant residence, where sophisticated design and modern amenities create a welcoming atmosphere. The open-concept layout effortlessly connects the living room, dining area, and chef's kitchen, providing a fantastic space for entertaining or simply enjoying quality time with loved ones. The heart of this home is the gourmet kitchen, featuring sleek granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a large center island with seating, and ample cabinet space. It's a culinary enthusiast's dream, perfect for crafting memorable meals. Step outside to discover your own private oasis. The professionally landscaped yard showcases a beautifully designed patio area for al fresco dining, a lush lawn for play and relaxation, and flourishing garden beds for your green thumb to flourish. The attached two-car garage provides convenience and additional storage space, ensuring your vehicles and belongings are kept secure. Nestled in the heart of Green Valley Ranch, you'll enjoy the best of both worlds — a peaceful suburban setting and easy access to urban amenities. Parks, schools, shopping, dining, and entertainment options are all within your reach. Don't miss the opportunity to make 19417 Randolph Place your forever home. Schedule a showing today and experience the pinnacle of Denver living. Your Denver dream home is within reach. Act now and embrace a life of luxury, style, and comfort in this exceptional residence.
